<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880722-0158 </DOCNO><HL> Textron Gets Navy Helicopter Job Valued At $146.9 Million </HL><SO> </SO><CO> TXT TRW GE </CO><IN> ARO </IN><G> DEF </G><DATELINE> WASHINGTON  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Bell Helicopter Textron, a unit of Textron Inc., received a $146.9 million Navy contract for production of AH-1W helicopters.    Units of TRW Inc. were given contracts totaling $71.1 million for information-system services for the Air Force and a computer-data network for the Navy.    Units of General Electric Co. won contracts totaling $36.9 million for aircraft-engine development services for the Air Force and aircraft-engine parts for the Navy. </TEXT></DOC>